title: 01/27/2021 - Best of The Herd

description:
-The Rams are openly taking shots at Jared Goff for a reason

-If the Patriots were NSYNC is Tom Brady the Justin Timberlake and Bill Belichick the Lance Bass?

-Aaron Rodgers talks to the media because he's isolated in Green Bay

-Tom Brady will need a couple breaks to beat Patrick Mahomes


Guests: Dave Wannstedt, former Dolphins & Bears Head Coach

Tyler Dunne, former Packers Beat Writer
